body: This sounds like a toddler having a tantrum about his tantrums not being well received.  FYI, anyone can report anything. Additionally, automod is programmed with profiles of objectionable behviour, and will remove such posts without human intervention.  No system is perfect, which is why we have modmail to reach out to the moderators. And which is why tantrums like this one are poorly received.  If you‚Äôre getting stomped on, chances are very high the problem is with you, and not everyone else.
